title: Celine Nano Belt Bag
description: Celine nano belt bag in light taupe grained calfskin leather. Featuring a top leather handle, gold-tone hardware, and belt detail at the front. The top flap and the zipper closure opens to a suede calfskin lining interior. Approximate dimensions: 20cm(L) x 18cm(H) x 11cm(D), 9cm handle drop, with an adjustable and detachable strap drop 57cm. Accompanied by a Celine dustbag. With Entrupy Certificate of Authenticity. (Pre-owned)
